    "The models were trained on a mixture of CoNLL, MUC-6, MUC-7 and ACE-named entity corpora.",
    "The basic required output tags are \"PERSON\", \"LOCATION\" and \"ORGANIZATION\" [83].",
    "spaCy 64 is implemented in Python.",
    "No detailed information is presented related to its model.",
    "The related output tags include \"PERSON\", \"LOC\", \"ORG\", \"GPE\" etc."
